    "body": "The previous version of complement only support Var in itermark. In this pr we allow expression to support a generic complement computation. For fragment layout, we set _rep to [0,1) to avoid var based check.\n\n<!-- This is an auto-generated comment: release notes by coderabbit.ai -->\n## Summary by CodeRabbit\n\n* **Bug Fixes**\n  * Simplified fragment-index handling for improved efficiency\n  * Improved iterator computation and unused-iterator division via expression simplification\n\n* **Tests**\n  * Added test covering kernel construction and non-variable iterator-mark scenarios\n\n* **Chores**\n  * Updated third-party submodule pointer\n\n* **Chores / Tooling**\n  * Enhanced debug/print output for iterator expressions\n\n<sub>✏️ Tip: You can customize this high-level summary in your review settings.</sub>\n<!-- end of auto-generated comment: release notes by coderabbit.ai -->",
